  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>China‚Äôs State Council in late January <a href="http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/china/2013-01/30/c_132139588.htm">approved</a>  an ‚Äúenergy consumption control target‚Äù to keep the country‚Äôs total energy consumption below the equivalent of 4 billion tonnes of coal per year by 2015.</p></div>
