  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>LBNL ChinaFAQs Expert Nathaniel Aden analyzes China‚Äôs revised energy production, consumption, and intensity data covering the years 1996 to 2008.  Aden found the changes and implications to be significant.</p>

<p><a href="http://china.lbl.gov/publications/initial-assessment-nbs-energy-data-revisions">Read the full analysis</a></p></div>
