                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/chinafaqs-experts-testify-chinas-green-energy-and-environmental-policies-us-china-economi">ChinaFAQs Experts Testify on China‚Äôs Green Energy and Environmental Policies before the US-China Economic and Security Review Commission, April 8, 2010</a></span>
