  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>ChinaFAQs Experts <a href="http://www.chinafaqs.org/expert/rob-bradley">Rob Bradley</a>, <a href="../expert/jennifer-turner">Jennifer Turner</a>, <a href="http://www.chinafaqs.org/expert/stephen-hammer">Stephen Hammer</a>, and <a href="../expert/angel-hsu">Angel Hsu</a> testified before the US-China Economic and Security Review Commission on April 8 to lend insight into both China‚Äôs domestic and international Green Energy and Environmental Policies.</p>

